caption:
Setting the expectations !
-
When you set the expectation, you set the blueprint in the tone of the rest of the conversation. When you eliminate objections straight off the bat, by breaking down what you were there to do and how you plan to do it, allows you and the homeowner to both be on the same page of what this process looks like!
